2007;;That Beautiful Somewhere;;Canadian;;Robert Budreau;;Roy Dupuis, Jane McGregor, Gordon Tootoosis, David Fox;;crime melodrama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/That_Beautiful_Somewhere;;A detective teams up with a young female archaeologist to unravel the mysterious death of a 'bog body' found in a native swamp rumoured to have curative powers. It is the story of two wounded souls searching for healing and redemption.